Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:22:03.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}All my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:45.99,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}講究女人魅力的我在你眼中 (Rather)
