Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:58.89,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}這樣一遍遍的讓你  心懷意亂 故作鎮靜 浮想聯翩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:02.71,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}無論是誰  就算是他或是別人 (So give me more)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.30,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}即使不擅長爾虞我詐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.50,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}但是不出手就不會滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.99,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}深深刻在心中的 (Program)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:17.94,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}戀情或是愛慕 (Monogram)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:20.73,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}今天一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.66,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}給我一個回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.76,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}將「喜歡」的心意傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:33.90,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be5}只有我這麼做不會很可笑嗎?
